---
name: Microservices request flow
category: Web
tags: [microservices, gateway, cache, database]
description: Client → API gateway → service → cache + database. The bread-and-butter web architecture.
---
# Microservices request flow

nodes:
  - id: client,  kind: actor,   label: Client
  - id: gateway, kind: gateway, label: "API Gateway", sub: "auth · rate-limit"
  - id: orders,  kind: service, label: Orders, sub: v1.4
  - id: cache,   kind: cache,   label: Redis
  - id: db,      kind: store,   label: Postgres

edges:
  - client  -> gateway, label: "HTTPS"
  - gateway -> orders,  label: "POST /order"
  - orders ..> cache,   label: "read"
  - orders  -> db,      label: "write"
